OL,4,G1600FOklahoma!
OL,5,     GIn Oklahoma territory at the turn
OL,6,     Gof the 20th century, two young
OL,7,     Gcowboys vie with an evil ranch
OL,8,     Ghand and a traveling peddler for
OL,9,     Gthe hearts of the women they love.
OL,10,G1840FIconic Women Of Country
OL,11,     GIconic Women Of Country opens up
OL,12,     Gthe music vaults to provide an
OL,13,     Gintimate look at legendary female
OL,14,     Gartists, their stories and songs
OL,15,     Gand why they've stood the test of
OL,16,     Gtime.
